description:
Matt Biilmann, CEO and Co-founder of Netlify kicks off Jamstack Conf Virtual with a State of the Jamstack address. Learn about how far the technology has advanced in the last year, exciting new features, tools and services that have launched, as well as what's to come in the future for the Jamstack. 

Presented by Matt Biilmann, CEO and Co-founder, Netlify - https://twitter.com/biilmann 

Brought to you by Netlify (netlify.com) - Jamstack Conf Virtual 2020 https://jamstackconf.com
title: State of the Jamstack Oct 2020 Keynote, Matt Biilmann of Netlify
